Package: wipwn
Version: 1.0
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: root-repo
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, python, wpa-supplicant, pixiewps, iw, openssl, sudo, openssh
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/anbuinfosec/wipwn
Description: Fast automated WiFi WPS PIN cracking tool
 WiPWN automates the discovery and cracking of WPS‑enabled access points.
 It supports multiple attack modes: Pixie Dust, brute force, dictionary,
 and includes session management, vulnerability detection, and report generation.
